    <p style="width: 90%; margin-top: 1%;">Instructions will mention QR codes. Note, no direct links from hints to QR Code pages!!! But I'm adding a symulink from here to show structure of site. Pretend that landing on QR Code 1 was triggered by scanning the first QR code. Solving that cipher will take you to next hint, even if it hasn't been released yet.</p>
    
    
    </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
